383
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:13,600
I have my own plans.

384
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:16,030
No need for you to worry.

385
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:22,070
But I still have to remind you to not foil your whole plan just for her.

386
00:35:19,060 --> 00:35:21,790
